{"lemma":"قُرْبَةُ","slug":"قُرْبَةُ","root":"ق.ر.ب","root_slug":"ق-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"قُرْبَة","root":"قرب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35388","n35395","n35396","n35398"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"water container"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bladder"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bagpipe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"kinship"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See جِرَاب (jirāb)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35388","headword_ar":"قرّبهُ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoriybN","text_ar":"تَقْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused, to be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become, near, caused to approach,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew, near, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb. *) [Hence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~aba A@ll~`hu daAraka","text_ar":"قَرَّبَ ا@للّٰهُ دَارَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see in what follows.] ―         -b2-  [And hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to be a near associate; he made him an object of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took him into, favour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (agreeably with an explanation of the pass. in the Ham p. 184)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered him, an object of honour."},{"kind":"text","text":"] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~abahu minohu","text_ar":"قَرَّبَهُ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a king, or a governor, or prince, [or any other person who was either a superioror an equal,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made him to be to him a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobaAn","text_ar":"قُرْبَان"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. [a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near associate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a consessor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a particular,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"special, associate"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"companion"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobaAnN","text_ar":"قُرْبَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~abahu A_ilayohimo","text_ar":"قَرَّبَهُ اـِلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur li. 27, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He presented it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offered it, to them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he placed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put it, before them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) And one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr~b","text_ar":"قرّب"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSomahu A_ilaY Als~uloTaAni","text_ar":"خَصْمَهُ اـِلَى السُّلْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placed, his adversary before the Sultán"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rfE","text_ar":"رفع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr~b lil~`hi qarobaAnFA","text_ar":"قرّب لِلّٰهِ قَرْبَانًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He offered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"presented, to God, an offering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O: in the Msb,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"اـِلَى ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hay~aA waqar~aba","text_ar":"حَيَّا وَقَرَّبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoriybN","text_ar":"تَقْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hay~aAka A@ll~`hu waqar~aba","text_ar":"حَيَّاكَ ا@للّٰهُ وَقَرَّبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAraka","text_ar":"دَارَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God preserve thee alive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prolong thy life, and make thine abode to be near"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A, O, K:) one says thus of a host to a visitor. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aqoriybu","text_ar":"التَّقْرِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The denoting nearness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mughnee and K * voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awo","text_ar":"اَوْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and Kull pp. 82 and 83 and 124.) Thus what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSogiyru Alt~aqoriybi","text_ar":"تَصْغِيرُ التَّقْرِيبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The diminutive denoting nearness"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is such as occurs in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAriY qubayola Almasojidi","text_ar":"دَارِى قُبَيْلَ المَسْجِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[“ My house is a little before the mosque ”]. (Kull p. 124.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The advancing an argument in such a manner as renders the desired conclusion a necessary consequence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MF.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain sort of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eadow","text_ar":"عَدْو"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"running"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, O, K) of a horse: (S, O:) one says, of a horse,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr~b","text_ar":"قرّب"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoriybN","text_ar":"تَقْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised his fore legs together and put them down together"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in running:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he ran"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pelting the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his hoofs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (AZ, TA:) and it is also said of other animals than the horse: but not of the camel: (MF:) [one sort of]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Altqryb","text_ar":"التقريب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [a rate] less than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHuDoru","text_ar":"الحُضْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, O;) and more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxababu","text_ar":"الخَبَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (El-Ámidee, MF:) there are two sorts of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tqryb","text_ar":"تقريب"},{"kind":"text","text":", called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaY","text_ar":"اَعْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gallop"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adonaY","text_ar":"اَدْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a canter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) the former is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~aEolabiy~apu","text_ar":"الثَّعْلَبِيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_iroxaA='u","text_ar":"الاـِرْخَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  See also 1, near the end, in two places."}],"source_refs":["Jel","A","O","K","S","AZ","TA","MF"]},{"entry_id":"n35395","headword_ar":"قُرْبَةٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaruba","text_ar":"قَرُبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.: and used as a simple subst. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nearness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobN","text_ar":"قُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the former is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in station,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grade,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rank."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talabotu minohu Alqurobapa","text_ar":"طَلَبْتُ مِنْهُ القُرْبَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sought of him nearness of station,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"admission into favour"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraAbapN","text_ar":"قَرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  Also, (A, O, Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurubapN","text_ar":"قُرُبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any righteous deed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereby one seeks nearness, to bring himself near, to draw near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to approach, unto God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to advance himself in the favour of God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * O, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobaAnN","text_ar":"قُرْبَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, Msb, K:) pl. of the first and second"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurabN","text_ar":"قُرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobaAtN","text_ar":"قُرْبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurubaAtN","text_ar":"قُرُبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurabaAtN","text_ar":"قُرَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["A","O","Msb","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n35396","headword_ar":"قِرْبَةٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaA='","text_ar":"سِقَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, * O, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waTob","text_ar":"وَطْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is used for milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes for water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is sewed on one side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [the modern"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is seldom, if ever, used for anything but water, is (if I may judge from my own observations and the accounts of others) always made of the skin of a goat about one year old or upwards: it consists of nearly the whole skin; only the skin of the head, and a small portion of that of each leg, being cut off: it has a seam extending from the upper part of the throat nearly to the belly, and sometimes a corresponding seam at the hinder part, but more commonly only a patch of leather over the fundament and navel: over the seam, or over each seam, is sewed a narrow strip of leather; and a mouth of leather is added in the place of the head: it is carried on the back, by means of a strap, or cord, &c., one end of which is generally attached to a cord connecting the two fore-legs; and the other, to the right hind leg:] the pl. (of pauc., S, O) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobaAtN","text_ar":"قِرْبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirabaAtN","text_ar":"قِرَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiribaAtN","text_ar":"قِرِبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and (of mult., S, O)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirabN","text_ar":"قِرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","ISd","K"]},{"entry_id":"n35398","headword_ar":"قُرُبَةٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobapN","text_ar":"قُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraAbapN","text_ar":"قَرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}